content: No rooms match this filter. Try a different one or clear filter to view all rooms.

comment.text: "No rooms match this filter. This message is displayed when a user searches for rooms that don't meet their criteria and is typically shown on an empty screen after clearing filters or changing search parameters."

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'təmiz filtri sınayın' is slightly awkward. 'Təmizləyin' (clear) would be more natural than 'sınayın' (try).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Bütün otaqlara baxmaq üçün fərqli filtri və ya filtri təmizləyin.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation uses a colon (:) after the first sentence, which is not typical in Armenian. It's more natural to use a period (.) or a conjunction.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ոչ մի սենյակ չի համապատասխանում այս ֆիլտրին։ Փորձեք մեկ այլ կամ մաքրեք զտիչը՝ բոլոր սենյակները դիտելու համար։

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrasing 'մեկ այլ կամ մաքուր զտիչ' can be improved for better flow.  'կամ' (or) implies a choice, but cleaning *one* filter is not a choice. It's better to suggest clearing all filters or trying a different one.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Փորձեք մեկ այլ ֆիլտր կամ մաքրեք բոլոր զտիչները

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ' appears to have a typo. It should likely be 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While understandable, the phrasing 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງທີ່ຈະແຈ້ງ' could be more natural. It's a bit literal translation of 'clear filter'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ລົບຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "escolha limpar os filtros" is slightly awkward. A more natural phrasing would be "limpar os filtros".
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nenhum quarto corresponde a este filtro. Tente um filtro diferente ou limpar os filtros para ver todas as salas.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Filtru de sală nu a produs rezultate' is a literal translation of 'Room filter did not produce results'. A more natural Romanian phrasing would be 'Nici o sală nu se potrivește cu acest filtru' or 'Nici o cameră nu se potrivește cu acest filtru'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nici o sală nu se potrivește cu acest filtru.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'ştergeţi filtrul' is grammatically correct but sounds a bit formal. A more casual and user-friendly alternative would be 'curățați filtrul'.
The word 'පෙරහන' is repeated and while technically correct, it feels slightly repetitive. Consider rephrasing for better flow.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: මෙම පෙරහන් වලට ගැළපෙන කාමර නැත. වෙනත් පෙරහන් යොදා ගන්නා, හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට හිස් කරන්න.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට හිස් කරන්න' could be improved for natural flow. While grammatically not incorrect, it's slightly clunky.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: හෝ සියලුම කාමර බැලීමට පෙරහන් හිස් කරන්න.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "zrušte ho" is a slightly awkward translation of "clear filter". A more natural Slovak phrasing would be "vymažte filter" or "vynulujte filter".
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Tomuto filtru nezodpovedá žiadna miestnosť. Ak chcete zobraziť všetky miestnosti, skúste iný filter alebo ho vymažte.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'филтер' is consistently used. The correct spelling is 'филтер'.
The sentence "Ниједна соба се не поклапа са овим филтером" could be slightly improved for a more natural flow. While grammatically correct, it sounds a little stilted.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Није пронађено ниједне собе које одговарају овом филтеру.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "se ne poklapa" is slightly awkward. A more natural phrasing would be "ne odgovara" or "ne odgovara uslovima filtera".
The word 'obrišite' (delete) isn't the best fit for 'clear' in this context. 'Pobrišite' or 'Uklonite' would be more suitable.
